title: Bobcats complete sweep of Lady Jacks
text:
Bobcats complete sweep of Lady Jacks By: Uncredited Report Error 
The Brandon University Bobcats women’s basketball team swept aside the Dakota College-Bottineau Lady Jacks with ease in pre-season play at the Healthy Living Centre on the weekend. 
Shayna Mathison put up 12 points on Sunday in the Bobcats’ 84-49 victory. Mikaela Stanton, who will redshirt this season, Kinsley Ransom, Keisha Cox, Amy Williams and Lauren Anderson all chipped in with 10 points for the home side. 
On Saturday, the Bobcats beat the Lady Jacks 87-58. No statistics were available.
